json.label: crossroad
json.name: Crossroads
json.description:
You end up at a crossroads, there is a sign here.
↑   Perion
→   Ellenia
↓   Henesys
←   Kerning City.

json.name: Construction Site Floor 1
json.description:
A chaotic maze of half finished steel scaffolding.

Wooden beams are used to close the gaping holes between the floors.

A large skeletal framework of a construction site is here.

json.name: A clearing
json.description: An open clearing nestled among towering trees, where the natural canopy forms a breathtaking ceiling of leaves and branches, many of which challenge you to climb them. Houses and shops are built high in the trees, connected by a series of wooden bridges that sway gently in the breeze.

json.name: The Mage's Tavern
json.description: A thick scent of aged honey mead and fresh forest herbs lingers in the air, blending with the subtle, earthy aroma of damp moss.

json.name: The tree trunk
json.description: A large tree towers over you, its roots shaped as stepping stones for you to approach the trunk. there is a large oval shaped hole in its bark.

json.name: Tree branch
json.description: The tree branch is thick and sturdy, its rough bark beneath your feet providing a firm grip as you balance high above the ground.

json.name: Rope bridge
json.description: The weathered wooden planks creak whenever you make a step as you cross from one towering tree to another. A rope ladder is dangling from the above you.

json.name: Tree branch
json.description: The tree branch is thick and sturdy, its rough bark beneath your feet providing a firm grip as you balance high above the ground.

json.name: The tree top

json.name: A dark room
json.description:
Welcome to JORM!
Type @tip"look"@back to look around.
Find the exit and @tip"go"@back there!

example: @tip"go north"@back

json.name: Another dark room
json.description:
There is a piece of paper on the ground. 
Pick it up with @tip"get [item]"@back.

Then identify it with @tip"identify [item]"@back

json.name: Northern wall
json.description: There is a small hole in this wall.

json.name: South-west corner
json.description:
There is someone else here.
You can talk to npc's with @tip"talk [npc name]"@back

json.name: Inside a hole
json.description:
This place looks like some sort of nest for a large animal.
Luckily all that is here is just a tiny mouse.

Type "fight" to start a fight
Type "use swing on mouse" to use your swing skill to kill it.
